  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Dick</b> is a common male name and nickname in Westeros. It may refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Beardless_Dick\" title=\"Beardless Dick\">Beardless Dick</a>, a member of the brotherhood without banners</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Fletcher_Dick\" title=\"Fletcher Dick\">Fletcher Dick</a>, an outlaw in the Kingswood Brotherhood</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Yellow_Dick\" title=\"Yellow Dick\">Yellow Dick</a>, one of the Bastard's Boys</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dick_Bean\" title=\"Dick Bean\">Dick Bean</a>, a man-at-arms in service of House Targaryen in 42 AC</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dick_Cole\" title=\"Dick Cole\">Dick Cole</a>, a sellsword in the Golden Company</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dick_Crabb\" title=\"Dick Crabb\">Dick Crabb</a>, called \"Nimble Dick\" a former soldier from Cracklaw Point</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dick_Follard\" title=\"Dick Follard\">Dick Follard</a>, called \"Deaf Dick Follard\", a ranger of the Night's Watch</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dick_Straw\" title=\"Dick Straw\">Dick Straw</a>, a sellsword in the Windblown</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dick&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Dykk_Harlaw\" title=\"Dykk Harlaw\">Dykk Harlaw</a>, an ironborn raider</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dickon_Flowers\" title=\"Dickon Flowers\">Dickon Flowers</a>, the Bastard of Beesbury</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dickon_Frey\" title=\"Dickon Frey\">Dickon Frey</a>, son of Ser Jammos Frey</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dickon_Manwoody\" title=\"Dickon Manwoody\">Dickon Manwoody</a>, son of Lord Dagos Manwoody</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dickon_Morrigen\" title=\"Dickon Morrigen\">Dickon Morrigen</a>, who fought in the Last Storm</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dickon_Tarly\" title=\"Dickon Tarly\">Dickon Tarly</a>, son and heir to Lord Randyll Tarly</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Richard_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Richard (disambiguation)\">Richard (disambiguation)</a></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404015052\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.004 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.004 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:14714-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404015052 and revision id 266679\n -->\n",
